'''Stan Sakai''' (born [[May 25]], [[1950s#1953|1953]]) is a Japanese-American comic-book writer and artist best known for the long-running series ''Usagi Yojimbo''. Sakai wrote and pencilled the ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' story "[[Urchins]]," and was the letterer for the ''Tales'' story "[[Spare Parts (comic story)|Spare Parts]]."{{Mediacat|imagecat=Images by Stan Sakai}}

